name: QVine
0:
”Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next quarterly meeting?”
”Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next holiday?”
”Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next corporate activity?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: q vine
des: The QVine app allows you to ask about upcoming events on the QVine calendar. You can ask about the quarterly meetings, picnic, holiday party, other corporate activities and holidays.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
